# LXR Mailbox — ASCII banners (mandatory)

- **Never remove** the multi-line ASCII “LXR” banner block (`██` art) or the wolves.land separator / copyright footer from script file headers.
- **When adding a new** `.lua` (or other script) file **or** opening a file that has no banner: **create** the full standard header to match existing files in this resource (see `server/helpers.lua`, `config.lua`, or `client/services/helpers.lua` for the canonical pattern).
- Refactors and cleanups must **leave banners intact**; only add or extend comments below the banner if needed.
